# Plan: Apply MEGnet Implementation from Backup to Main Project

## Status: ALL STEPS COMPLETE

## Context

The `MEGqc_backup/` directory contains a complete MEGnet integration that allows using MEGnet's ICA-based classification to generate synthetic ECG/EOG reference signals. This is useful when no physical ECG/EOG channels are available, or as a fallback when recorded/reconstructed signals are poor. The main project (`meg_qc/`) currently has no MEGnet support. This plan ports all megnet-related changes from the backup into the main project, preserving the main project's newer features (epoching_strategy, session handling, settings panel, 2D sensor support, etc.).

